{"TopicId":187314,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"So KSP 2 just got announced...","CreatedByName":"4x4cheesecake","CreatedById":187982,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:26:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"4x4cheesecake","CreatedById":187982,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:26:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m watching the opening night stream for the gamescom in germany right now, and just a few minutes ago, KSP 2 was announced for the next year. So far, just a cinematic trailer but it loos like the same universe (Duna was clearly visible, also Laythe and Jool) and a quiet a few fancy parts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/P_nj6wW6Gsc?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m a little bit hyped \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003Eedit: almost faster then \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/187313-we-are-excited-about-kerbal-space-program-2/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ethe official forum announcement\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-19T18:27:43Z\u0022 title=\u002208/19/2019 06:27  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 19, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by 4x4cheesecake\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"netbumbler","CreatedById":146001,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:35:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah if they can get the graphics anywhere near the quality of the trailer, then they can take ALL my money!\u00A0 lol\u00A0 Actually, I just want a new game engine with better orbital mechanics simulation and get rid of the GC stuttering. But nicer graphics will be appreciated...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Athen","CreatedById":189381,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:43:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187314\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566239745\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146001\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022netbumbler\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, netbumbler said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah if they can get the graphics anywhere near the quality of the trailer, then they can take ALL my money!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey\u0027ve released a few pictures on the official ksp website, and it looks similar, minus the ray-tracing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"l0kki","CreatedById":182979,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:46:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSQUAD NO!!!!11!!1!111!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xurkitree","CreatedById":187694,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:53:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder if we\u0027ll get Life Support lmao\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn seriousness though, I hope they optimise this well for poor gpu\u0027s. I would love to play this withough stutter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOTHER THAT THAT IM FRICKING HYPE LETS GO\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"basbr","CreatedById":21492,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:54:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni am curious to see how this will turn out but in the back of my mind there are two questions.\u00A0how much of the dev team is as passionate as the early squad team was. and how much is\u00A0take-two\u00A0gonna screw it up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nim very afraid that\u00A0take-two will start meddling in it. dumbing it down to appeal to a wider audience, add\u00A0microtransactions, rushing the development (ksp 1 has taken years to get where it is and is still not finished and now probably never will be)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand i hope that\u00A0ksp 2 is not just\u00A0a sticker they slapped on the old one as a quick cash in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni love ksp but i am afraid it will be mangled and lose all the things that make it unique\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theJesuit","CreatedById":122369,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T18:55:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like TakeTwo have followed their Civ release model.\u00A0 GAME \u002B expansion pack 1 \u002B expansion pack 2\u00A0 then GAME 2.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DH8SpaceWolf","CreatedById":189999,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:16:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:22px;\u0022\u003EOOOOOOOOOOOOOOH MYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY GOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOD\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Levelord","CreatedById":57711,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:17:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHYPEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steuben","CreatedById":77368,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:19:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTwo words\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPre. Order.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother two words\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nValue. Pack.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLast three words.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMerch. And. Dising.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s dising... and how does one do it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:21:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just remade all my favorite ships\u00A0in \u00A0KSP1 ...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not like it\u0027s bout to drop tomorrow though,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Greatness101","CreatedById":171504,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:23:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com/game/kerbal-space-program-2/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com/game/kerbal-space-program-2/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck the website, we\u0027re getting advanced parts, colonization, and INTERSTELLAR TRAVEL\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:23:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653140\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187314\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566242462\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002259717\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tw1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Tw1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just remade all my favorite ships\u00A0in \u00A0KSP1 ...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not like it\u0027s bout to drop tomorrow though,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m going to keep playing KSP 1 alongside the new game for a while at least. I have so many mods and other stuff that\u2019s going to take some time to reach KSP 2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jon Tash","CreatedById":2681,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:24:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m geeking out right now so hard!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:27:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653147\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187314\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566242593\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m going to keep playing KSP 1 alongside the new game for a while at least. I have so many mods and other stuff that\u2019s going to take some time to reach KSP 2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI had some fanworks I\u0027m going to reopen and finish off. There are lots of long runners in the fanworks subforum too. I hope this won\u0027t cause problems there, making them all look so outdated\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbolExplorer","CreatedById":177191,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:29:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe hype...ITS OVER 90000\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0