22 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022009ORvk.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002225.06\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/009ORvk.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMULTIPLAYER!??? how did I miss that...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Richy teh space man","CreatedById":12511,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:39:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm wonder if aliens will be added too if interstellar travel is a thing\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NHunter","CreatedById":190849,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:43:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid I just see Orion and Deadalus drives (and another thing-that-looks-like-a-fusion-torchdrive)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T19:50:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmmmm... Looks like they still didn\u0027t fix the lander legs. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. Looks like I\u0027m going to Gamescom this week...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Johnster_Space_Program","CreatedById":187334,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T20:31:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, after seeing the trailer for KSP 2, what did you think of it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought it was amazing seeing how different it looks from KSP 1, it seems like the graphics got a update and there is going to be more you can do along with playing with friends (I think multiplayer is a good addition). Now i\u0027m wondering what the title screen will look like.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat about you?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-19T20:33:03Z\u0022 title=\u002208/19/2019 08:33  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 19, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Johnster_Space_Program\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T20:33:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOverlapping threads have been merged.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PrvDancer85","CreatedById":180954,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T20:58:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInterstellartravel and building colony stuff even on console sounds pretty awesome to me. Lets hope for a good start\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FreeThinker","CreatedById":117389,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T22:16:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223653472\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187314\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566248328\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022180954\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PrvDancer85\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, PrvDancer85 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInterstellartravel and building colony stuff even on console sounds pretty awesome to me. Lets hope for a good start\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder where they get their inspiration from.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheJoolian","CreatedById":199427,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T23:09:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen i see the trailer i was overhyped.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}